# golden-rules/skill.md installs mandatory security standards into CLAUDE.md.
# It references these terms in an educational, advisory context (e.g. "never store
# plaintext passwords", "use env vars for API keys"). These are not active
# exploitation instructions — they are the rules developers must follow.
\.env\b
credentials
api[_-]?key
secret[_-]?key
access[_-]?token
private[_-]?key
password
